    <p>I am a certified Syrian Second Officer with over 46 months of professional sea service aboard general cargo and bulk carriers, currently serving on MV DENIZ ID. I proudly represent Syrian seafarers on international platforms and aim to voice their challenges and aspirations globally.</p>

